snippet.title: Dooming The Bar V1.1 Trailer
snippet.description:
Download here:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1DQipiuNiXjT8MTbhrkk9_32LEgJljKPR/view
https://www.mediafire.com/file/egj9a6a31bg6gew/DTB_V1.1.zip/file
Follow my Twitter: https://twitter.com/ChiefSmokey1
Join my Discord: https://discord.gg/S8jaGfw

Dooming The Bar is a project centered on bringing the Half-Life 2 beta's City 17 into Doom, composed of a fully playable 8-map journey from the Industrial sector through to Kleiner's lab as per 2001 and 2002 concepts, plus two bonus maps.
